{"tid":1847740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"封關一賠五十, 遣返支那畜一賠一百","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T08:05:45.000Z","uid":47356,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e177a29767ef70b68ed5eeb8497103921f3a527","tid":1847740,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"用緊急法拉罷工既醫護 一賠二<br />\n用緊急法分李嘉誠身家 一賠一萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回應五大訴求,加解散黑警, 切柒煲湯派街坊"},{"pid":"87314cc9855f6829b64ff5a4d92d341dd4d117ac","tid":1847740,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4ae3518a1c41d93ba6dba2a665cfc23f40a0d7","tid":1847740,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"買定離手"},{"pid":"3543d543cf7b218781f98e34b512f2e8cff29293","tid":1847740,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8d289bcbac6534076522a3aebebb17c5826e78a","tid":1847740,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34e9892b2cad275f58837b9a1be10210bb44b8c","tid":1847740,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72345824ebc071519ce289113a4d10a6ff25ebb6","tid":1847740,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"宣佈下台一賠幾"},{"pid":"7d44fd7c41ccdb93b7a472d28bee12132e7b4f9f","tid":1847740,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"叫大收皮<br />\n<br />\n緊急法延長假期"},{"pid":"2578035be766e1fd90a9075fc7334b982ebd44d6","tid":1847740,"uid":36455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"想分誠仔買落嘅口罩酒精糧水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de95d4a5744738fb1685dec3891d6a7592d96cc9","tid":1847740,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"加強接收大陸患者1賠1.01?"},{"pid":"4a4a493fe845ba083ba0b0cefea2e7f648b1265b","tid":1847740,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d44fd7c41ccdb93b7a472d28bee12132e7b4f9f","tid":1847740,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"叫大收皮<br />\n<br />\n緊急法延長假期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:47:46.000Z","msg":"一賠幾好"},{"pid":"83ce9ccfe4c187aeaa77b1e8f908cdc5fdf9cc5a","tid":1847740,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,